{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was with one of the Berlin firms, and I don't know the name of it, but I wouldn't be surprised if, pre-Nazi days, it may not have had one or another Jewish member.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think he had Catholic affiliations, Kubuschok, because he represented von Papen, who was a big Catholic leader in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Kubuschok was low-keyed, and he never made any of the major kind of Nazi defenses like there's no law that governs us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're another bastard just like us, which was one of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Concentrate on the facts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was on pretty good terms with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'd kibbutz in the corridors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember talking to him about the case at one point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, oh, you've got a terrible case, he said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you knew what I knew, you'd have a good case.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he spoke pretty good English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To illustrate the kind of relationship I had with him, we-- there was some good-looking German girl who showed up in our courtroom all the time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say our courtroom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were mainly commission hearings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whenever there was anything going on, she'd be there, and my assumption was that she was a, a relative of the defendant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, why else would anybody want to listen to turgid testimony about banking operations?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at one recess, I said, who's the blonde back there?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, oh, you want to meet her?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll introduce you at the next recess, and he did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was a rather nice girl, good looking, who was not Nazi at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a-- she was actually an Austrian news reporter covering the trial for some Viennese paper, but she was German, not Austrian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her family was Nazi inside and out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
